Package: DNMBcluster
Title: Pan-Genome Clustering Results Visualization
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Jae-Yoon", "Sung", email = "k2dydwl@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R-side reporting and visualization for the DNMBcluster pan-genome
    pipeline. Reads DNMB-native Parquet outputs produced by the Python
    clustering stage and generates flower plots, pan/core curves, phylogenies,
    and combined HTML reports. Absorbs and modernizes the BPGAconverter code
    base.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.2)
Imports:
    arrow,
    ggplot2,
    ggnewscale,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    tibble,
    magrittr,
    scales
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
